Package: dfdb.RODBC
Type: Package
Title: Access Data Tables in an RODBC Data Base as Pseudo-Dataframes
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2008-11-29
Author: John Fox and Oswaldo Cruz
Maintainer: John Fox <jfox@mcmaster.ca>
Depends: RODBC
Description: This package contains functions that allow the user to treat data
  tables in an ODBC-accessible data base as if they were data frames, including
  the ability to access subsets of the rows and columns of the table and to
  modify the table; row "subscripts" can be specified as SQL queries.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes
